00:02:38.305 --> 00:02:41.425
I'm going to go for a red value of 230,

00:02:41.425 --> 00:02:46.820
225 for the green and 225 for the blue.

00:02:46.820 --> 00:02:50.405
This is going to give us this light white color,

00:02:50.405 --> 00:02:53.990
which will take effect for all of our body section.

00:02:53.990 --> 00:02:56.825
To find out more about these particular color values,

00:02:56.825 --> 00:03:00.360
we can do a search for HTML color picker.

00:03:00.500 --> 00:03:03.900
There is various color pickers which you can see online,

00:03:03.900 --> 00:03:06.980
or this default one which comes with the search engine.

00:03:06.980 --> 00:03:09.515
We can see for any shade which we select,

00:03:09.515 --> 00:03:11.755
have a red, green, and blue value,

00:03:11.755 --> 00:03:15.110
