this will be pushed over.

00:03:42.220 --> 00:03:43.710
Let's just check this.

00:03:43.710 --> 00:03:46.400
This will be pushed over on the left of the project.

00:03:46.400 --> 00:03:49.235
But now with the auto value on the left and right,

00:03:49.235 --> 00:03:52.870
